              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two hyperpure germanium detectors, ORTEC,",
                "nominally 20% photopeak efficiency relative to a 3 x 3\"",
                "NaI(Tl) scintillator"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Si-surface barrier detector monitor was",
                "placed at 45-degree to the beam direction for",
                "normalization.",
                "The relative gamma-ray efficiencies were determined",
                "with a Eu-152 radioactive source."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A self-supported 1-mg/cm**2 thick enriched Pd-110,",
                "more than 97%, foil was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma-rays and beamlike particles were",
                "        measured in coincidence"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 15.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in the relative normalization",
                "between the lowest and highest energy measured to be",
                "no more than 15%. This is a systematic error that could",
                "not be evaluated very precisely and for this reason,",
                "has not been included in the uncertainties presented in",
                "the figures."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " No information on sources of uncertainty"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The angular distribution parameters, necessary for",
                "correcting the yields at the fixed gamma-detector",
                "angles, were calculated by the code considering upper-",
                "level feeding, the geometry and absorbers of the",
                "detectors, the integration over the beam-energy",
                "variation through the target and the deorientation due",
                "to the hyperfine interaction of the recoil in vacuum."
              ]
            }
          ],
